{"tid":1540673,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋對港共總結咗五大訴求出嚟，對對國際社會嘅求救又可唔可以總結成五大請求？","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:43:18.000Z","uid":34154,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a56fe1c8c76b0779b4b1f2bd6c00038587888b7","tid":1540673,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"香港五大訴求 Five demands in Hong Kong<br />\n1. 完全撤回逃犯條例修定法案 Full withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. 獨立調查黑警濫暴 Independent inquiry into alleged police brutality<br />\n3. 撤回暴動定性 Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo;<br />\n4. 釋放政治犯/示威者 Amnesty for arrested protesters<br />\n5. 全面落實雙普選 Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and<br />\nthe Chief Executive<br />\n<br />\n對國際社會五大請求 Five requests to the international community<br />\n1. 就香港警暴問題提供人道救援 Provide humanitarian aid in response to police brutality in Hong Kong<br />\n2. 制裁破壞香港人權官員 Sanction persons/government officials who violate human rights in Hong Kong<br />\n3. 通過香港民主及人權法案 Pass Hong Kong Democracy and Human Rights Act<br />\n4. 確認支共違反英中聯合聲明 Confirm China's breach of Sino-British Joint Declaration<br />\n5. 重新審視香港主權 Review the sovereignty over Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n當然我哋對向國際社會發出五大請求嘅時候，就應該唔可以叫五大訴求缺一不可咁大口氣，我覺得可以humble d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efa9c234aadffbe6e19e6bde01ad0656485525e","tid":1540673,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab86b7957be3e4ad1292fddf0537c3a7de6c40c","tid":1540673,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re